description: It never seemed right that the cheese that represents our nation-American cheese-was not actually cheese, but processed cheese food (what the heck is that, anyway?). It took some time and a lot of experimentation to get our recipe right, but we've finally come up with a cheese that has the mild, melty cheesy goodness kids love, with none of the emulsifiers that worry parents.
